column3: “I am beyond proud of this bowl size to high level ratio. I just wanted to take a slight edge off so I packed a third of a bowl and hit it well and yup -- baked. Master Chef (High Files) ability with this high: I just made the best PB&J sandwich of my life; super chunky peanut butter, peach amaretto butter, and peach apricot spread on French bread.”

“White Diesel is an interesting strain. It has a definite sativa high to it, but has just enough of an indica feel to it to allow for you to relax completely to some music or a film. I've found the high only lasts around an hour and a half, but it doesn't leave you feeling burned out afterwards like a more indica heavy strain would. This strain isn't going to get you to a 10/10 high easily, but it's great for unwindin...”

“i'm always looking for a good daytime strain and this seems to do the trick. it checked in at 22.%thc for a sativa. The previous reviews led me to believe this was a clear headed daytime work" strain
column5: thanks guys! I believe this was $12 a G pre-tax $60 for 4G. For the price and the head which is totally "daytime" it's freakin great! Actually gives me a pep and makes me want to do stuff!. As f...”"

column3: “Chocolate chip is my flavor when it comes to cookies but I'm obsessed with THIS cookie flavor now!! Raspberry Cheesecake Cookie 🍪 from Gaia's Gift 🎁! So delicious!!! I tend to prefer Indica dominant but this was a Real Treat =)”
“Sweet taste with a calming day time resting affect.”
“One of the best strains I've ever had. Bud was nice and leafy, smelled wonderful, and the effects are euphoria and overall happiness.”
“I like the smell but find myself smoking more often because the high doesn't last very long. While it last (it really doesn't) its cool.”

“Wow! This high brings me back to my high school days. Really energetically calm and euphoric.  Extremely long lasting. 2 to 3 hours of smiles. The pain of a long  hard day eased away! Smells pungent diesel and kinda buttery pine. Taste like fuel and butter with good earthy exhale. Im going back to get more tomorrow!!!”

“Wow! This high brings me back to my high school days. Really energetically calm and euphoric.  Extremely long lasting. 2 to 3 hours of smiles. The pain of a long  hard day eased away! Smells pungent diesel and kinda buttery pine. Taste like fuel and butter with good earthy exhale. Im going back to get more tomorrow!!!”
“Absolutely love this strain! The body high flows well with the heady high. Philosophy major after a bowl of this. Just a nice chilled high, but it really doesn't make thee sleepy.”
“Loved it!! Perfect for video games:)”

“This is a great strain. I highly recommend it, I've smoked for 12 almost 13 years, and this is one of my tops. It has a strong smell, but not overbearing, you smell the diesel but get a hint of lemon as well. It has a sweet, earthy taste that's light. beautiful buds. Takes effect fairly quickly, mellow, and relaxing but with energy still to get things done. Decreases stress and opens up creativity and keeps you focus...”

“I'm a HUGE sativa fan. Indica's are my go to for bedtime. I'd love to give this a full 5 stars but it's hard. I feel like it has enough indica to kind of make me lazy, not sleepy, but lazy. It makes it hard to smoke this during the day when I have to always be on the move. It's not bad though. I love the smell and taste.”

“Fantastico. The initial heavy diesel taste of this indica dominant strain is quickly overcome with floral tones of dried flowers and asian spices. A lovely high of mainly couch lock but still enough motivation to venture into the outside world.”
“Love it . Great taste. Super strong smell. Rooftop high.”
“Its like sour mixed with mob or something its a good high and great flavor”
“OMG this killed me strong diesel aftertaste wonderfull mental high and alertness”
“tasty af”
“very average high. nothing special”
“good sativa dominant. makes you get out and do stuff or you can just chill out like an indica!”

“Wonderfull!! 

Had some plants and all came out just fine!! 

Nice and relaxing experience with White Diesel!!”
“One of my all time favorite strains. It hits hard and is great for armchair philosophizing.”
“White Diesel started me out with a very relaxing buzz, and then it made me hungry.  Decent chronic pain relief and made me sleepy to boot. Had me focused and a light euphoric presence.”
“Its like sour mixed with mob or something its a good high and great flavor”

“best strain i've ever grown and smoked. very strong strain that could take all circumstances when grown in and outdoor. the buzz is just ehat you are looking for, a clear head and takes off your stress. White Diesel and Sour Diesel forever <3”
“Love it . Great taste. Super strong smell. Rooftop high.”

“Fantastico. The initial heavy diesel taste of this indica dominant strain is quickly overcome with floral tones of dried flowers and asian spices. A lovely high of mainly couch lock but still enough motivation to venture into the outside world.”
“heavy hitter taste great heavy body high one off my top picks”
“nice taste,,gd high got my headaches & migraines gone... 202 soufside hood review gd gas #Highlife”

“White widow X NYC diesel..40% sativa 60% indica..very nice piney lemon scent , i just open the jar and it smells everywhere....like no other. Nice smoke during the day feels energetic you wanna do stuff. A must try!!”
“A very nice go to diesel strain. Smoke can be harsh, and tastes of diesel and pine. Great strain for lazy days and relaxing after work as it works wonders for pain and sleeplessness.”
“Had some of this and it is a good day time use for later in the day.”

“first time trying this strain.. So far my thoughts on it is that, I really enjoy this strain. for me it has a nice mellow effect, definitely get a lil chatty. So I would recommend it for a social setting. No anxiety, which I know is a plus for some people.”
“Tried. Little effect.”

“The smell of this strain is what hits at first, since it is awfully pungeant and pervasive. The buds were not that dense but dried out rock-solid. Thricomes forms during tha last two weeks a frosty ice-cap (hence the name white" diesel
column4: I suppose). The taste is strong
column6: and acid. The buzz hits real fast : you don't even have to wait for the third toke to known for sure that now
column8: you're in for good. Yet it...”"

column3: “Totally will fuck you up. It's crazy good. It was grown indoors so you know it's good ;) this cali shit is the bomb! I highly recommend it :)”
“Eh...nice smell and taste. Smooth smoke but doesn't last long enough for me.  Wouldn't get it again.”
